'''Migaama''' (also known as Migama, Jongor, Djonkor, Dionkor, Dyongor, Djonkor About Telfane) is an [[Afro-Asiatic languages|Afro-Asiatic]] language spoken in central [[Chad]].<ref name=e18/>
